00:14:36,550 --> 00:14:38,000
But it was me

323
00:14:38,030 --> 00:14:39,720
who took up e-sports

324
00:14:40,030 --> 00:14:41,000
as a profession and a dream.

325
00:14:46,510 --> 00:14:48,320
So in a relationship,

