in front of the computer for hours,

344
00:15:48,670 --> 00:15:51,080
just tapping a few keys back and forth.

345
00:15:52,550 --> 00:15:53,030
Of course.

346
00:15:53,630 --> 00:15:54,630
Ai Jia doesn't understand

347
00:15:54,670 --> 00:15:55,630
