546
00:25:42,310 --> 00:25:43,640
She and I had a long talk

547
00:25:44,750 --> 00:25:45,550
about you,

548
00:25:46,070 --> 00:25:47,110
about e-sports,

549
00:25:48,030 --> 00:25:49,750
about this business of yours.

